 cơ \"mượn\" con voi từ đoàn xiếc của bạn gái. Tuy nhiên, anh ta vô tình làm mất con voi và bị cuốn vào vòng xoáy của vụ án tiền giả...</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"233962","season":1,"vote_average":9,"vote_count":2},"modified":"2025-10-16T14:26:51.000Z","cast":["Li Jiuxiao","Tương Long","Ma Yinyin","Dư Ngai Lỗi","Mao Tao","Ren Ke"],"director":["万力"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Li Jiuxiao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Li Jiuxiao","tmdb_id":1724347,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wBaTXTKFCavDhHleVBZ1F35DWfS.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1724347"},{"name":"Tương Long","name_vi":"Tương Long","name_original":"Jiang Long","tmdb_id":2970787,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hA1cl7W79METFqHv8Vf4JfPxkbI.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2970787"},{"name":"Ma Yinyin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ma Yinyin","tmdb_id":1396636,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oCFD2FbNLHR15cwMCuFfPpkQHn6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1396636"},{"name":"Dư Ngai Lỗi","name_vi":"Dư Ngai Lỗi","name_original":"Yu Ailei","tmdb_id":1387956,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nuyaR00afCkuwMXts1Mpc7Wycqg.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1387956"},{"name":"Mao Tao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Mao Tao","tmdb_id":4553132,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/njjVMhq2KuEeX3DRlxqxJNhCVk4.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4553132"},{"name":"Ren Ke","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Ren Ke","tmdb_id":3676098,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qYLXFYCs3V5OkFOq65KDGr44iHe.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3676098"}],"keywords":[],"pubjs_url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gotvtop102/pjs102@main/pubjs/da/dai-tuong-bien-mat.json"}